property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    'ReceiveIncomingPayment' || '::' || "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID"                AS "ID",
    "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Time"                                                           AS "Time",
    "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ChangedBy"                                                      AS "ExecutedBy",
    "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ExecutionType"                                                  AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem_Changes"
        ON "ReceivableItem"."ID" = "ReceivableItem_Changes"."ObjectID"             
WHERE "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Attribute" = 'IncomingPayment'
    AND "ReceivableItem_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "ReceivableItem_Changes"."OperationID" IS NOT NULL
